snippet.title: Soulstice – E3 Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Visit http://soulsticegame.com for extended gameplay access and exclusive content.

Fight in synergy as Briar and Lute, a powerful Chimera, as they seek to reclaim the sacred city of Ilden in Soulstice. Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1602080/Soulstice/
